annotations.description: Today we're doing a banana daiquiri Julie Reiner style! And if you don't KNOW who Julie Reiner is you better learn about it! This is just a wonderful wonderf...
annotations.title: Julie Reiner's Banana Daqiuiri NUFF SAID!!!!

textContent:
1oz (30ml) Jamiaca Rum
1oz (30ml) White Rum
1oz (30ml) Banane du Bresil
.5oz (15ml) Lime Juice
.5oz (15ml) Demerara Syrup (1:1)
1 Peeled Banana 
1.5 Cups (approx 12oz) Crushed/Pebble Ice
Caramelized Banana Garnish

Blend and pour into large coupe
